flowchart TD
    A[Enter Staff ID] --> B[Enter Password]
    B --> C[Login]
    C --> D[LDAP Authentication]
    D --> E{Valid?}
    E -- Yes --> F[Encrypt password into session]
    F --> G[Store encrypted key in session cache]
    G --> H[Response Returned]
    E -- No --> I[Invalid Username or Password]
    I --> J[Return Error]